data.name: ENQUIRE
data.description: Expanding Networks by Querying Unexpectedly Inter-Related Entities

evidence: README indicates network usage: "- **IMPORTANT NOTE**: it is highly recommended to get an **NCBI API_KEY** before running ENQUIRE. [Getting one is very easy](https://support.nlm.nih.gov/knowledgebase/article/KA-05317/en-us). You can "
"ENQUIRE reconstructs and expands co-occurrence networks of genes and biomedical ontologies from user-selected input corpora and network-inferred PubMed queries."

"ENQUIRE can currently run on LINUX systems and LINUX virtual machines using Apptainer/Singularity and on Linux, MacOS, and Windows using Docker." and the implementation table links to a Docker image: "https://hub.docker.com/r/muszeb/enquire"
